        studentLife:'The University of Sevilla has 70,000+ students and is one of the oldest in Andalusia. Student social life revolves around outdoor terraces (terrazas) and Friday tapas bars. Triana is the hub for Erasmus students. Rent is very affordable — typically €300–500/month for a room.',
